      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tew buhs ar teem Aâ-\nn taunu Brahli / un wiꞥna\nehlus ar wiꞥnu/ apgehrbt/ un\nv buhs tohs fwaidiht / un tew\nhs wiꞥnu Rohku pildiht / un\ns fwehtiht/ ka tee manni Pree-\ni effus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Darri teem arridsan linnu\nas/ wiꞥnu Meefas Plikkumu\naht/ no teem Gurneem lihos\nahn buhs tahm buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Aâronam/ un wiꞥna\nleem buhs tahs apwilkt / kad\nkfsch tahs Sa-eeschanas Telts\nt/ jeb kad teem pee ta Altara\nt/un ja-kalpo eeksch ta Sweig-\nka tee ne nosegahs un mirst/\nai irr weens Likkums wiꞥ-\n/ un wiꞥna Dsinmmunam\nwiꞥna/ muhscham.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad buhs tew Aâronu un\nwiꞥna Dehlus pee tahs Sa-ees-\nschanas Telts Durwin west / un\nbuhs tohs ar Uhdeni masgabt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz to buhs tew tahs Drehs-\nbes nemt / un Aâronam tohs\nschaurus Swahrkus un ta Eewo-\nda Uswalku / un to Eewodu / un\nto Kruhchu Glihtumu apwilkt/\nun wiꞥnam to Johstu kahrt to Ee-\nwodu apjohst.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhs to Zeppurins\nwiꞥna Galwn lift / un tahs\nSwehtibas Krohni buhs tew pee\ntahs Zeppures lift.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhs to Swaidi-\nschanas-Etji nemt / un us wiꞥna\nGalwn leet: ta buhs tew wiꞥnu\nfivaidiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz to buhs tew wiꞥna\nDehlus arri atwest/ un teem tohs\nSwahrkus apwilkt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tohs ar to Johstu ap-\njohst/(prohti) Aâronu un wiꞥ-\nna Dehlus / un tew buhs teem\ntahs Zeppurites usfeet / ka teem\ntas Preestern-Ainmats effirs/par\nweenu Likkumu muhscham / tad\nbuhs tew Aâronam to Rohku pil-\ndiht un wiꞥna Dehleem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhs to Wehrfenu\natwest preekfch tahs Sa-eesch-\nnas Telts/ un Aâronam/ un wiꞥ-\nna Dehleem buhs farwas Rohkas\nus ta Wehrjena Galwn lift.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhs to Wehrfenu\nnofaut ta KUNGA Preekfchâ/\n"
    }
